{"tid":392932,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"Dell XPS15 (GTX) 定 Precision 5520 (Quadro)","createTime":"2017-09-09T00:14:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-15T00:49:01.000Z","uid":46487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"deba35a49ad7ff771e108117ef24496f785a5c05","tid":392932,"uid":46487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T00:14:55.000Z","msg":"XPS15 $14400<br />\nPrecision 5520 $14280<br />\n<br />\nShare Spec:<br />\ni7-7700HQ<br />\n16GB DDR4-2400Hz<br />\n15.6&quot; 1920x1080<br />\n<br />\nXPS: GTX1050<br />\nPrecision Quadro M1200<br />\n<br />\nXPS: 512 PCle SSD<br />\nPrecision: 256 PCle SSD+ 1TB HDD 5400rpm<br />\n<br />\nPrecision: Mobile Intel CM238 (唔知有咩用)<br />\n<br />\nXPS: win10 home<br />\nPrecision: win10 pro(都係唔知有咩用)<br />\n<br />\nArchi 撚, 上網睇Quadro GPU 係專業繪圖用，但係只有係solidworks 方面有拋離 (但係我唔用soildworks <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nCAD Rhino Maya GIS Adobe 方面好似冇乜直接數據支持，唯一吹奏之處就係穩定性高啲，咁究竟值唔值得揀Quadro?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n原價方面precision 5520 成三皮野都唔知做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樣又差唔多Spec 又差唔多XPS15 原價都唔洗兩皮，有冇巴打洞悉到個玄機？"},{"pid":"6940ea840efe8086b680ff77d065a7b96236233e","tid":392932,"uid":71564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T01:27:18.000Z","msg":"睇你用途啦，普通使用或打機咪xps。專業繪圖個啲咪precision<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nquadro 通常用黎做高階既cad 因為佢用既driver 係opengl 同一般gtx 既direct3d 黎比，好似係一啲專業既rendering 個方面會做得好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><a href=\"http://www.velocitymicro.com/blog/geforce-vs-quadro-whats-the-difference/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.velocitymicro.com%2Fblog%2Fgeforce-vs-quadro-whats-the-difference%2F&d=vAB8B4lwwixEeVJmoS8wNjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=bcf00